## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **milasen 2018 (Yu Boston Children NEJM 2019)** = first FDA n-of-1 ASO. Mila Makovec (CLN7 Batten MFSD8 splice-site mutation). 1 patient → custom ASO 설계 → IND → 투여 → biomarker improvement → seizure 감소. n-of-1 era 의 historical 시작점. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-ASO 결합 modeling 직접 fit.
2. **N-Lorem Foundation 2019- (Crooke)** = Ionis founder Stanley Crooke 이 설립한 non-profit. n-of-1 ASO 무료 제공. 2024 50+ patients enrolled. ASO mfg cost (~$1M+ per patient) 의 access barrier 해소.
3. **FDA 2021 guidance "Individualized ASO Drug Products"** = first regulatory framework for n-of-1. single-patient IND pathway 의 normalization. 임상 evidence 기준 = single-patient before-after + objective biomarker.
4. **atipeksen + jacifusen 2020-2021** = Boston Children 2nd + 3rd n-of-1. ATM (A-T) + FUS-ALS. milasen pipeline 의 reproducibility 입증.
5. **KIF1A.org cohort (N=10) 2023+** = patient advocacy organization 이 ASO design 주도. KIF1A motor domain mutation-specific. n-of-N (small cohort) pattern emerging.
6. **Beam BEAM-101 + Verve VERVE-101 base editor** = HBB sickle + PCSK9 cardiovascular. cohort scale 이지만 single-edit precedent. n-of-1 에서 single-edit base editor 의 in-vivo 적용 (CBE A→G + ABE) 가 ASO 보다 정밀.
7. **NTLA-2001 (Intellia ATTR in-vivo CRISPR) 2021+** = single-dose in-vivo CRISPR. trial scope (cohort) 이지만 per-variant guide RNA design 가능 → n-of-1 으로 확장 가능.
8. **Charlie Gard MDDS 2017** = controversial compassionate IND. UK NHS + Vatican + US Trump 정치화. n-of-1 윤리적 + 보험 + cost + access 의 cautionary tale.
9. **NIH Bespoke Gene Therapy Consortium (BGTC) 2023+** = NIH 8 ultra-rare disease pilot. AAV gene therapy n-of-1 platform. 1-2 환자 IND-enabling FDA pathway 의 institutional support.
10. **wet-lab + RCT impossible by definition** — n-of-1 = single-patient. RCT 가 부적용. quantum-only in-silico 가 design support 의 ideal niche. FDA 2021 guidance 의 evidence 기준 = pre/post biomarker + mechanism plausibility.

